node.text:
Living in Florida the sun is just too strong for me to spend a lot of time outdoors. So here’s how I create a sun kissed look with beauty products ☀️ 

✨ @juviasplace Color 1 eye primer 
✨ @reinarebelde Coqueta face trio 
✨ @benefitcosmetics Roller Liner in Brown 
✨ @fentyskin Hydro Vizor SPF 30 sunscreen 
✨ @lauramercier Secret Camouflage Duo on 4N
✨ @fentybeauty Eaze Drop skin tint in shade 11 
✨ @nyxcosmetics Can’t Stop Won’t Stop contour concealer in the shade Mahogany 
✨ @maccosmetics Ginger Spiked Quicktrick stick 
✨ @narsissist Radiant Creamy Concealer in Light 2.6 
✨ @makeupforever R230 powder lightly set just under my eyes to avoid creasing 
✨ @toofaced Better Than Sex mascara 
✨ @nyxcosmetics Brown lipliner 
✨ @liveglam Paris liquid lipstick 
✨ Hair colored by @gizelle_stylesorlando 

#makeup #makeuptutorial #juviasplace #reinarebelde #fentybeauty #fentyskin #benefitcosmetics #lauramercier #nyxcosmetics #maccosmetics #toofacedcosmetics #nars #makeupforever #liveglam

node.title: Want that sun kissed look without having to bake in the sun? 😬

node.text:
THIS IS NOT SPONSORED 🗣 I had to give my hair some TLC, because Christmas had me feeling like a 🧟‍♀️ Here are the products I used...

1) @notyourmothers Curl Talk Cleansing oil to remove build up on my scalp then I rinsed it out 
2) @notyourmothers Curl Talk Deep Conditioning Curl Masque...I let that sit for about 30ish minutes 
3) I then detangled my hair starting at my ends and then working my way up using a @denmanbrush 
4) After washing the conditioner out my hair I applied the @notyourmothers Curl Talk Leave in Conditioner really focusing on my ends 
5) To style I use @notyourmothers Curl Talk Defining Cream & Frizz Control Sculpting Gel (I scrunched that into my hair) 
6) Using my @dysonhair Diffuser I diffused for about 20 minutes then I stopped to separate some of my curls that clumped up together 
7) After separating my curls I went back to diffuse for 10 more minutes 
8) Once my hair was fully dry I used my hands to fluff my hair. Fluffing is the key to having really voluminous hair. I don’t mind a bit of frizz with volume. Some people prefer more definition and less volume/frizz. It’s a preference thing! 💗💗💗💜💜💜

Hope this helps!!! XO #notyourmothers #curlyhair #naturalhair #healthyhairjourney #healthyhair #dysonhairdryer #dyson #denmanbrush

I know #Halloween this year feels strange, but thanks to @Messenger, there is a super spooky way to get together with your family and friends while being physically apart! 🎃👻 Messenger has been rolling out a collection of exciting new artwork and AR experiences to make this #spookyszn extra fun! 👏🏽 This look was inspired by the neon skull effect. There’s so much Halloween inspiration in Messenger. You guys HAVE to check it out!!! 🖤🧡
Head to my stories for more.

node.text: Who’s an OG follower & remembers when I used to post before/after pics of my clients? 👀🥺 I haven’t taken clients in years aside from the occasional family or family friends. node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kay-Lani on July 19, 2021 tagging @sheinofficial. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: I remember when I used to post so many #ootd pictures 😩 (I don’t even know if we still use that hashtag anymore or not. That’s how long it’s been for me 🤣)…but then I had 2 kids and my appearance became more of an afterthought for me 🥴 But I really missed who I was before becoming a mom of two so I’ve been trying to make more of an effort to get dressed up. I don’t have time for hair, makeup and dressing up so when my makeup and hair are done I’m dressed down & when I’m dressed up I have my hair in a bun and no makeup on. Oh well!!! Cheers to small wins 🥂 Dress is from @sheinofficial & shoes are from Shoe Land…whole outfit cost me about $25 🙌🏽🎉
